{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grid container","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Container","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>通过设置 CSS 属性 <code>display:grid;</code> 或 <code>display:inline-grid;</code> 可以将一个元素定义为<strong>网格容器</strong>(<strong>grid container</strong>)，并且它的所有直接子元素都会成为网格项。</p>\n<p>网格容器会创建一个<strong>网格化环境</strong>(<strong>grid firmatting context</strong>) 。它的直接子元素通过定义 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a> 和 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a> 属性可以将自己变为<em>显式网格</em>，当某个元素不在显示网格内时，它就会变为<em>隐式网格</em>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更过","title":"了解更过","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性参考","title":"属性参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\"><code>grid-template-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\"><code>grid-auto-rows</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid\"><code>grid</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"扩展阅读","title":"扩展阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS 网格布局：<em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">网格布局基本概念</a></em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更过","id":"了解更过"}],"summary":"通过设置 CSS 属性 display:grid; 或 display:inline-grid; 可以将一个元素定义为网格容器(grid container)，并且它的所有直接子元素都会成为网格项。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Grid container","locale":"en-US","native":"English